#ROOMS
#16053
#1Brujah Throne Room#n~
#0You have entered the Lair of the blood thirsty Brujah. Once created as
protection for an intelligent branch of Kindred, the Brujah grew to great
power. Even now they are feared as you glanced around the room, noticing
epic battles depicted in tapestries. There is a dim light somewhere in the
room, but the shadows seem to envelop everything. You get the feeling
that where you are standing is far from safe. On the furthest wall, you notice
a large throne, with a slightly smaller throne on either side of it. The Founder,
Suurge, sits in the middle surrounded by his Princes, Jaryth and Cruor. A
smell creeps by your nose, as you look down you notice a body lying in a
pool of blood. Something tells you it is the last fool to trespass.
~
