#16054
#1Brujah Portal Room#n~
#0Ancient magic swirls in this room, causing the shadows to dance with
delight. Cobwebs cover many feet of this room, but a large gate is left in
the center of the room. Before the gate stands a large granite post, which
seems to have something etched into it. It appears to be written in ancient
Kindred language. Everything is a dull grey with #1blood stains #0scattered
about. Large roars can be heard echoing through the Lair of Brujah, as you know
you are not alone. A large beast steps out from the corner, his fangs still dripping
with a deep red blood. You feel it is time to go...
~
